    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Runs once for all incoming items\n\nconst structured = items.map((item, index) => {\n\n  const title = String(item.json.title || \"Untitled Story\");\n  const impact = Number(item.json.impact_score || 0).toFixed(3);\n\n  const text = String(item.json.content || \"\")\n    .replace(/\\s+/g, \" \")\n    .trim()\n    .substring(0, 1200); // Hard cap per story\n\n  return `\nStory ${index + 1}\nTitle: ${title}\nImpact Score: ${impact}\n\nContent:\n${text}\n`;\n}).join(\"\\n------------------------------\\n\");\n\nreturn [\n  {\n    json: {\n      story_bundle: structured\n    }\n  }\n];"
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        1280,
        -272
      ],
      "id": "f949f029-7180-4302-b90d-aeec1a319e6d",
      "name": "16 Aggregate: Build Article Bundle"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "3230b3c8-5bd9-45f4-a923-3a5447c91df1",
              "name": "prompt",
              "value": "=`You are TrendScoop, an experienced local civic journalist.\nYou must ONLY use the information explicitly provided in the story inputs below.\nYou are NOT allowed to invent, assume, speculate, infer missing details, or introduce any facts not directly stated.\nIf something is unclear or incomplete, omit it.\nDo not generalize beyond the text.\n\nBelow are the structured story inputs:\n\n{{$json.story_bundle}}\n\nTASK:\nWrite ONE unified daily civic digest that synthesizes the key developments into a single professional briefing.\n\nSTRICT RULES:\n- Do not list stories separately.\n- Do not mention \"Story 1\", \"Impact Score\", or formatting labels.\n- Do not reference JSON.\n- Do not fabricate statistics, timelines, or officials.\n\nFORMAT EXACTLY AS:\nHeadline: <Clear professional headline summarizing the day>\n\nBriefing:\n4–6 concise paragraphs integrating the developments into a coherent local civic update.\n\nTone: Professional, factual, newsroom-style.`",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
